data.description:
Nice updated home in Olive Branch! Freshly painted inside and out!  New HVAC, water heater, window glass and new luxury vinyl flooring. The large primary suite is downstairs and private with a nice four piece bath with double vanity and large walk in closet. The family room has tall ceilings and nice architectural lines and the kitchen is spacious with a breakfast area and eat-in counter.  Upstairs are two additional bedrooms plus a supersized bonus room with new flooring .  This home is 2296 sq ft and sits on a .91 acre lot, has lots of windows and is open and airy! EZ access to the airport, FedEx Forum and all around.  

This home has been loved!
